  "text": "Secondly, did Franklin place the limitation on his physical body himself. I am Ra. This is partially correct. The basic guidelines for the lessons and purposes of incarnation had been carefully set forth before incarnation by the mind, body, spirit, complex, totality. If the one known as Franklin had avoided the excessive enjoyment of or attachment to the competitiveness which may be seen to be inherent in the processes of its occupation, this entity would not have had the limitation, however, the desire to serve and to grow was strong in this programming, and when the opportunities began to cease due to these distortions towards a love of power of the entities, a limiting a factor was activated.",
